Dialogue: 5,0:04:06.07,0:04:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,'Sup, Chisaki.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:07.72,0:04:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayama{-kun}!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:09.66,0:04:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can give you a lift.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:11.77,0:04:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking about stopping by Saya Mart on the way home!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:14.38,0:04:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Good timing, then.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:23.15,0:04:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Egawa's getting married.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:25.60,0:04:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:26.89,0:04:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He knocked up some girl.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:28.20,0:04:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Knoc—
Dialogue: 5,0:04:30.19,0:04:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But will he be able to finish college?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:32.84,0:04:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems the girl's dad \Nis the president of some company,
Dialogue: 5,0:04:35.04,0:04:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,so he's gonna quit school and work for him.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:38.20,0:04:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in shock.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:39.68,0:04:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the surprise of the year.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:41.26,0:04:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he'll be back {replace}in January{for the \Ncoming-of-age ceremony}, though.{coming-of-age ceremony: a japanese thing. once a year in january every who turns 21 (or 20?) that year in a certain area gathers and theres a ceremony or something}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:44.34,0:04:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We all plan on teasing the crap outta him.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:47.25,0:04:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's changed so much,
Dialogue: 5,0:04:49.44,0:04:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's only been five years.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:51.16,0:04:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're the one who's changed the most.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:53.28,0:04:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:53.77,0:04:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there's a rumor going around \Nthat you're, like, some lonely housewife.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:58.57,0:04:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kinda hot.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:59.73,0:05:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:03.59,0:05:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late, young man!{}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:05.74,0:05:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me you weren't out playing pachinko again!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:08.97,0:05:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Just went out for some fresh air.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:10.45,0:05:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The boss has been waiting on you, you know.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:14.19,0:05:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{Oh, }Chisaki!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:15.46,0:05:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:17.33,0:05:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Akira{-kun}. I got this for you.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:22.15,0:05:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, what do we say?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:23.76,0:05:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Fanks.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:28.29,0:05:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out, Akira!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:32.68,0:05:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He never listens to anyone but Miuna.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:35.43,0:05:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's such a headache!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:37.79,0:05:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:39.91,0:05:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,it's thanks to her that he's here.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:45.71,0:05:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The people of the sea can hibernate, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:49.01,0:05:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari{-kun} and everyone else \Nare probably just asleep, then.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:51.79,0:05:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. They're definitely okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:54.58,0:05:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't—
Dialogue: 5,0:05:55.14,0:05:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not the problem!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:58.21,0:05:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Akari?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:01.31,0:06:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I can have this baby right now.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:05.04,0:06:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Having a baby is a blessing.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:07.22,0:06:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't talk like that.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:09.12,0:06:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. Just leave me alone.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:12.13,0:06:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Akari—
Dialogue: 5,0:06:12.80,0:06:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Just go away! Please.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:23.73,0:06:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Miuna?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:26.86,0:06:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Miuna...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:28.73,0:06:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna be a boy.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:33.05,0:06:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:39.85,0:06:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A boy, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:42.51,0:06:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:44.48,0:06:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I'm really happy.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:46.80,0:06:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy that I'm gonna \Nhave a little brother.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:49.95,0:06:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Mom.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:04.37,0:07:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Akari{-san}?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:06.13,0:07:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, i-it's nothing.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:07.56,0:07:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{replace}Up your butt{Kancho}.{this is some game japanese kids play, youll have to look it up on wikipedia.}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:14.02,0:07:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Akira!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:16.17,0:07:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:17.34,0:07:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been obsessed with that lately.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:19.18,0:07:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's okay...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:20.54,0:07:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, get back here, you dummy!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:22.63,0:07:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:22.63,0:07:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh? You got in one of your \Nspecial {replace}{kancho }attacks, did ya?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:24.26,0:07:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I said,{technical comma splice} don't move! Hey!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:25.32,0:07:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Run!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:42.17,0:07:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Miuna.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:44.59,0:07:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mi-u-na.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:46.18,0:07:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice try, Sayu.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:50.57,0:07:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Miss Miuna.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:53.45,0:07:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Teacher.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:55.65,0:07:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You remind me of your uncle, you know.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:57.87,0:07:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:59.10,0:08:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,When you sleep, I mean.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:00.34,0:08:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari used to sleep in class a lot too.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:02.08,0:08:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:02.96,0:08:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, today's the day \Nof the long-awaited Tomoebi.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:06.83,0:08:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,In the past, you couldn't see it \Nunless you were at the bottom of the sea.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:10.80,0:08:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And while it was the sun \Nback then, it's the moon now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:15.43,Chalk Pusher Is Pushing It,,0,0,0,,{\fsp2\blur0.5\fscx123\fscy107\pos(655,58)\c&HEADFD5&\1a&H9B&}Tomoebi
Dialogue: 5,0:08:14.31,0:08:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that the sea is frozen, the ice acts like a prism
Dialogue: 5,0:08:17.70,0:08:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and gathers light from all the saltflake snow.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:20.40,0:08:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This projects an image onto the night sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.77,0:08:25.27,Chalk Pusher Is Pushing It,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fscx58\fscy61\c&HF4EBE1&\1a&H4E&\move(130,23,69,23,31,4494)}Tomoebi Before
