Dialogue: 5,0:08:22.74,0:08:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,making an illusory moon.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:25.27,0:08:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So the best time to see it is when the moon's at its lowest... at about eight o'clock.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:30.65,0:08:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{replace}Teach{Sensei}! And before that?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:33.87,0:08:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:35.10,0:08:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Dinner!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:36.74,0:08:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,After this, it's time for rations!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:40.27,0:08:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Having a meal by the sea with everyone...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:40.66,0:08:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Now, now, kids.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:42.60,0:08:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The main event is the Tomoebi.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:42.80,0:08:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bit nostalgic, isn't it?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:44.86,0:08:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't forget that, okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:46.07,0:08:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:47.45,0:08:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Having class at night is pretty exciting.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:49.88,0:08:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't that right, Minegishi?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:51.32,0:08:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, um... yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:58.37,0:08:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Be on your guard, Miuna!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:59.93,0:09:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:01.50,0:09:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I totally found out...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:03.62,0:09:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight during the Tomoebi,
Dialogue: 5,0:09:05.77,0:09:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Minegishi's planning to ask you out.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:08.45,0:09:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask me out...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:09.90,0:09:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's so lame.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:12.02,0:09:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,School's a place for studying!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:15.73,0:09:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayu, you used to hate studying.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:19.12,0:09:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've decided that I'm \Ngonna live on my own someday.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:23.04,0:09:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's not like I'm \Ngonna find work in Oshiooshi.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:26.66,0:09:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So I plan to go to the city \Nand become an independent woman.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:30.13,0:09:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You've planned that far ahead?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:32.72,0:09:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,More or less. What about you, Miuna?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:34.90,0:09:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not really sure yet.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:37.37,0:09:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I don't plan on leaving, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:40.39,0:09:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{Oh...}{this is hardly anything}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:52.31,0:09:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Miuna.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:53.40,0:09:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:54.52,0:09:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Your hair's gotten longer.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:58.11,0:09:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:59.85,0:10:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayu! Miuna!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:01.58,0:10:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The teacher's calling you!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:03.40,0:10:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:05.56,0:10:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Miuna.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:06.88,0:10:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:12.29,0:10:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{...s}Shouldn't you two be in school?{PV}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:14.90,0:10:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I used to {always }watch from here...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:16.97,0:10:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}just like this.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:20.65,0:10:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Akari!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:21.30,0:10:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Akari{-san}!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:21.84,0:10:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mukaido!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:22.32,0:10:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out! The bridge pier!{PV}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:22.54,0:10:25.34,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}No!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:26.25,0:10:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At that moment, I decided I wouldn't cry.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:31.18,0:10:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I mean, I knew Hikari and the others were in the sea.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:36.37,0:10:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had faith that they were safe
Dialogue: 5,0:10:39.29,0:10:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,950)\i1}and that they were still smiling, in a place I couldn't go.{if i recall correctly this is all one sentence originally}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:46.45,0:10:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:47.86,0:10:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! It smells delicious!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:49.92,0:10:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for being late.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:51.78,0:10:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me help.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:53.34,0:10:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. It's my turn today!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:58.65,0:11:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Your hair's {a little }wet.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:00.14,0:11:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to check under the sea again{ for a little bit}.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:03.00,0:11:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But something's in the way, so I couldn't see.{cant see the bottom / whats there / the others}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:05.42,0:11:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The sea temperature's gone down, too.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:08.03,0:11:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your tummy okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:10.30,0:11:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it is!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:11.76,0:11:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Being pregnant underwater is natural for us women of the sea{ and raised their young there}, you know.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:19.59,0:11:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not all bad.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:22.54,0:11:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:23.62,0:11:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,At least he's not alone. Dad's there with him.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:27.53,0:11:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, Hikari liked Manaka.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:31.05,0:11:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If Manaka and his other friends had been left in the sea and he'd been left alone out here,
Dialogue: 5,0:11:35.76,0:11:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet he wouldn't know what to do!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:38.82,0:11:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hikari... likes Manaka.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:42.51,0:11:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Careful, Miuna! It's about to spill over.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:45.67,0:11:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Safe.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:47.43,0:11:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fad(0,900)}He likes Manaka...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:51.17,0:11:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Miuna!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:53.40,0:11:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:54.58,0:11:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry! I'm coming!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:58.79,0:12:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even now, I'm here{,} watching,
Dialogue: 5,0:12:04.49,0:12:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}looking out at the sea where Hikari and the others are.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:24.87,0:12:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:26.72,0:12:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugu!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:29.57,0:12:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you two come \Nwarm up a bit before the Tomoebi?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:36.19,0:12:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:38.07,0:12:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This stewed golden eye snapper is delicious.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:40.62,0:12:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You just can't get food like this in the city!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:43.38,0:12:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:45.22,0:12:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:46.18,0:12:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh, nothing. I'm glad you like it.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:48.93,0:12:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The meat's good too.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:53.49,0:12:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to impose on you like this.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:56.04,0:12:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't be. It's livelier now, \Nso I'm glad you came.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:59.27,0:13:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to Tsumugu{'s} joining our lab, \Nour research has progressed quite a bit.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:04.57,0:13:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, there are only fourteen sea villages in all of Japan.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:07.62,0:13:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention, we can't set foot in any of them right now.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:13.21,0:13:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when we try diving to investigate,
Dialogue: 5,0:13:15.86,0:13:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the tide gets in our way,\N and we can't get close{ to the location}.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:19.30,0:13:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, there are even specialists saying that the sea villages no longer exist.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:24.15,0:13:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They're just saying that to get attention.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:29.53,0:13:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiradaira{-san}, I believe there is a close relationship between the surface and the sea.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:35.68,0:13:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So in order to make sense of the abnormal weather,
Dialogue: 5,0:13:37.84,0:13:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,we must research the sea villages as well.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:40.63,0:13:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:43.60,0:13:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me get you another one.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:45.66,0:13:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that would be wonderful.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:50.33,0:13:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a great girl.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:52.53,0:13:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}sure{\i0} there's nothing going on?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:55.14,0:13:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:56.96,0:14:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are at that age, though. \NAnd you're living under the same roof.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:00.32,0:14:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention, she's beautiful, which would usually mean—
Dialogue: 5,0:14:02.84,0:14:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There's someone else she's loved for a long time.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:07.28,0:14:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:12.03,0:14:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:16.88,0:14:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He can put out his futon himself.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:19.84,0:14:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a guest, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:21.72,0:14:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let him do that.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:24.11,0:14:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you come watch the Tomoebi with us?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:27.06,0:14:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:28.83,0:14:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point unless we all see the Tomoebi together.{this is a continuation of her earlier thought}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:33.26,0:14:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:35.67,0:14:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Since it's cold out, would you like me to make some {replace}rice wine{amazake}?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:38.74,0:14:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. That sounds good.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:46.99,0:14:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:48.46,0:14:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It really did turn into a huge deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.49,0:14:54.74,Oshit Oshit; Fishy Business,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\frx0\fry342\c&H6F1A01&\1a&H64&\fscx62\fscy62\pos(599,313)\org(589,456)}Oshiooshi Fishery Cooperative
Dialogue: 5,0:14:54.74,0:14:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We still haven't found the sea kids that fell in?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:57.40,0:14:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like this has never happened before.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:59.22,0:15:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe the sea god was this angry.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:01.65,0:15:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we gonna do about this girl?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:03.30,0:15:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She's got no relatives up here...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:04.70,0:15:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Chisaki{-chan}, you can—
Dialogue: 5,0:15:07.32,0:15:08.74,Alternative,,0,0,0,,You can come live with us.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:09.40,0:15:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:11.09,0:15:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Your apartment's cramped as it is.{talking to akari}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:13.90,0:15:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And besides...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:16.15,0:15:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from the sea too.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:21.75,0:16:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa! The lady next door \Nwanted me to give this to you.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:25.24,0:16:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandp—
Dialogue: 5,0:16:26.85,0:16:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:28.30,0:16:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, wake up! Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.17,0:16:32.67,This is No Brain Surgery,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.2\blur4\frx0\fry26\fscx85\fscy85\b1\frz349.5\pos(615,327)\alpha&H50&}In Surgery
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.17,0:16:32.67,This is No Brain Surgery,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.2\blur1\frx0\fry26\fscx85\fscy85\b1\frz349.5\pos(615,327)}In Surgery
Dialogue: 5,0:16:31.93,0:16:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're a family member,\N please wait over here.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:34.18,0:16:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Don't take Grandpa away!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:37.17,0:16:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Chisaki, calm down.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:39.12,0:16:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't leave me!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:40.53,0:16:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't take anyone else away from me!{Check timing}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:41.43,0:16:42.56,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Chisaki!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:44.72,0:16:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Chisaki.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:53.03,0:16:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, did you pack your underwear?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:55.72,0:16:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it. \NI'll do it myself.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:57.12,0:17:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely not. You're absent-minded when it comes to stuff like this.{Check timing}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:03.67,0:17:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're gonna be a college student in the big city...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:06.91,0:17:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And an oceanography researcher{,} to boot!{its an admirable thing to do, something to be proud of as she says in the next line, a good line of work. a respectable thing to do.}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:09.64,0:17:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be proud!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:11.17,0:17:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry that you ended up \Nhaving to take care of Gramps.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:15.83,0:17:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't even mention it. \NYou two are my other family.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:19.93,0:17:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're both precious to me.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:21.59,0:17:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Family, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:24.09,0:17:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:25.05,0:17:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,In the course of my research{ in college},
Dialogue: 5,0:17:28.79,0:17:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I plan to find out more about the sea villages as well as what happened that day.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:32.95,0:17:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they're somehow linked \Nto what's gonna happen on the surface.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:36.99,0:17:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugu...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:38.14,0:17:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they're fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:41.23,0:17:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And if everything takes a turn for the better,
Dialogue: 5,0:17:44.21,0:17:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure we'll see them again.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:49.73,0:17:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:01.99,0:18:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So good!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:03.22,0:18:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell? Mine's all potatoes!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:04.84,0:18:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry and finish eating!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:06.89,0:18:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tomoebi is about to start.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:09.81,0:18:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Minegishi, what about Shiodome?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:11.62,0:18:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:12.62,0:18:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:13.44,0:18:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:14.80,0:18:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to prove you're a man.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:16.44,0:18:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, boys are so stupid.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:18.30,0:18:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You done? I'll go put our trays to wash.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:19.90,0:18:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:29.89,0:18:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the currents.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:31.55,0:18:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems it's about to start.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:32.88,0:18:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:37.84,0:18:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ever since that day, the sea has been calm...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:41.43,0:18:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and perfectly quiet,
Dialogue: 5,0:18:43.72,0:18:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}never giving me a single clue \Nas to what's happening below.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:50.09,0:18:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiodome!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:56.39,0:18:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:58.59,0:19:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you asking me out?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:00.82,0:19:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Wh-Wha—
Dialogue: 5,0:19:03.78,0:19:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I may have jumped to conclusions. If so, just forget I said anything.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:07.20,0:19:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:08.71,0:19:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, let me say this first.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:11.58,0:19:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in love with someone else.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:13.67,0:19:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:14.92,0:19:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:18.75,0:19:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:19.86,0:19:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always been in love with you! \NEver since grade school!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:23.41,0:19:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't just give up!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:26.39,0:19:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't... just give up.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:27.04,0:19:28.56,Alternative,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I can't give up!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:28.56,0:19:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Who is he?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:30.50,0:19:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Please tell me!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:32.37,0:19:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:40.91,0:19:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiodome!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:11.81,0:20:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Tomoebi...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:13.20,0:20:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty magnificent, isn't it?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:15.61,0:20:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what is that?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:17.75,0:20:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Something big is showing up on the screen.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:19.68,0:20:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a fish?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:22.69,0:20:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where are you going?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:29.45,0:20:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Miuna, what are you...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:49.90,0:20:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:57.29,0:21:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He hasn't aged at all since that day.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:02.99,0:21:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not breathing!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:09.01,0:21:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think mouth-to-mouth \Nwill work on someone from the sea.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:21.47,0:21:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hika—
Dialogue: 5,0:21:25.41,0:21:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:30.51,0:21:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Who... are you?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:35.59,0:21:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Miuna.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:36.35,0:21:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Miuna?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:40.51,0:21:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumugu?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:51.89,0:21:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hikari's eyes{ that night}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:54.99,0:21:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}were frozen in sadness...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:57.73,0:21:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}just like the calm{ness} of the sea.
